OL,5,GBoth the main public service
OL,6,Gbroadcasters are celebrating big
OL,7,Gbirthdays. The BBC is marking its
OL,8,Gcentenary just as Channel 4 turns 40.
OL,10,FThere are certain parallels.
OL,12,FBoth face a degree of uncertainty about
OL,13,Ftheir future and finding the right way
OL,14,Fto mark the occasions may not have been
OL,15,Feasy.
OL,17,FThe BBC's centenary had seemed an
OL,18,Funderstated affair until now. A raft of
OL,19,Fspecial programmes over the past week
OL,20,Fhave played to its core audience.
OL,3,CBBC and Channel 4 in celebration mode
