OL,5,FFrom Strictly to the Antiques Roadshow
OL,6,Fthey have been a reminder of the ways
OL,7,Fthe BBC is at the heart of mainstream
OL,8,Fpopular culture.
OL,10,FThe special episodes of Doctor Who and
OL,11,FThe Repair Shop were a reminder of the
OL,12,Flove some have for the BBC and
OL,13,Fcomplemented the celebrations of the
OL,14,Fcentenary itself.
OL,16,FGetting the tone right can be hard. The
OL,17,FBBC itself means different things to
OL,18,Fdifferent people but has a collective
OL,19,Fstrength as an organisation.
OL,3,CBBC and Channel 4 in celebration mode
