OL,5,FIt's been interesting to see the use of
OL,6,Fa common ident for the anniversary
OL,7,Facross different channels. Again this
OL,8,Fsuggests each service is part of
OL,9,Fsomething bigger.
OL,11,FOver at Channel 4, the celebrations
OL,12,Fhave seemed more muted.
OL,14,FA revival of Friday Night Live was a
OL,15,Freminder of one part of its special
OL,16,Fpersonality. No doubt Countdown will be
OL,17,Fmarking its own 40th in style. (There
OL,18,Fwill be a little 40th birthday surprise
OL,19,Ffor Pres fans before Countdown on
OL,20,FWednesday.)
OL,3,CBBC and Channel 4 in celebration mode
