PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1669159331
OL,5,FPart of the channel's core audience
OL,6,Ftoday might regard a 40-year-old as
OL,7,Fover-the-hill.
OL,9,FAnother part of the public knows all
OL,10,Ftoo well that so many of the serious,
OL,11,Fchallenging programmes and minority
OL,12,Finterests which also ran through its
OL,13,FDNA are now seen less frequently.
OL,15,FWill there be any revival of the
OL,16,Foriginal idents? Well frankly reviving
OL,17,Fthe blocks has less of an impact now as
OL,18,Fit has happened so often.
OL,20,FMore seriously both organisations face
OL,21,Funcertain futures.
