OL,5,FSome opponents of privatisation had
OL,6,Fhoped that the plan would be shelved
OL,7,Funder Liz Truss. However during the
OL,8,Fsummer leadership contest Rishi Sunak
OL,9,Factively supported it. Watch this
OL,10,Fspace.
OL,12,FAs for the BBC, its celebrations are a
OL,13,Freminder that its core audience might
OL,14,Fbe prepared to fight for it. Any big
OL,15,Fdecisions won't come this side of the
OL,16,Fnext General Election.
OL,18,FBut anyone thinking radical thoughts
OL,19,Fmight be advised to look at the
OL,20,Faudience response to some of the
OL,21,Fcelebratory programmes.
